[img]http://i.imgur.com/SxmnIjb.png[/img]
Welcome to my Advertisement Thread on[b] Strattus-X,[/b] I am the Owner & Founder of Strattus and we have been online since March 22, 2014 and have been 24/7 with average of [b]15-30 players[/b]. It has been hard but fun, its always good to do something good to help the 614 community. We are planning on always being online at least for the next 2 years. If you used to play Strattus 2+ months ago I recommend to check it out now a lot of update improvements have been added.
[b]All new players that join will receive an extra 1B for joining from an Manager.
[/b][size=1.35em][b]Urls:[/b][/size]

[b]FORUM[/b]

-Mystery Boxes - 70+ Items Packed (20 Rares)
-Random Event Boxes - Same as Mystery Boxes but for Skillers
-Auto Vote System
-Vote Tokens
-Crystal Key Chest
-Safe PvP & Dangerous PvP (Along with Safe-Zones)
-Grand Exchange Home
-Custom Minigame Cave of Zaros
-Custom Mining Cave
-Skilling at Canifis
-Fishing in Development

-Vote for 2 hours of unlimited prayer + reward!
-No Vials when pking!
-Vengeance timer shows exact second
-Custom Quest tab
-WEEKLY UPDATES
